Text: "A day in Goa (India) with my friends, no money, no place to stay nothing to\
  \ eat but the only I have to survive here and watch what comes out....\n\nSuddenly\
  \ I met with a stranger, a local named Steven, he was very good and helped me more\
  \ than my friends with all the things like home, transport and transfer. \n\nThank\
  \ you\n Steven"
